## Safety Hook

**Git Guardrails** active via PreToolUse hook. Blocks:
- `git push` (all variants)
- `git reset --hard`
- `git clean -f/-fd`
- `git branch -D`
- `git checkout .` / `git restore .`

When blocked, you see "user has prevented you from doing this". Ask {{name}} to run manually.

